scripts.set-dev-env: eas secret:create --force --scope project --name APP_ENV --value development --type string
scripts.set-stage-env: eas secret:create --force --scope project --name APP_ENV --value staging --type string
scripts.set-prod-env: eas secret:create --force --scope project --name APP_ENV --value production --type string
scripts.build-ios-dev: yarn set-dev-env && eas build --platform ios --profile development
scripts.build-ios-stage: yarn set-stage-env && eas build --platform ios --profile staging
scripts.build-ios-prod: yarn set-prod-env && eas build --platform ios --profile production
scripts.build-android-dev: yarn set-dev-env && eas build --platform android --profile development
scripts.build-android-stage: yarn set-stage-env && eas build --platform android --profile staging
scripts.build-android-prod: yarn set-prod-env && eas build --platform android --profile production
scripts.build-all-dev: yarn set-dev-env && eas build --platform all --profile development
scripts.build-all-stage: yarn set-stage-env && eas build --platform all --profile staging
scripts.build-all-prod: yarn set-prod-env && eas build --platform all --profile production
scripts.update-all-env: yarn update:dev && yarn update:stage && yarn update:prod
